{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "vg-api-collection",
    "name": "VG API",
    "description": "API VG — http://localhost:3001\n\n**Criar conta para login:** usa **Auth > Signup** (ou registo no site). Não uses «Users > Criar utilizador» para testar login — esse endpoint é para admin.\n\n**Login:** envia JSON com `username` OU `email` + `password`. Exemplo:\n`{\"username\": \"sky\", \"password\": \"a_tua_password\"}`\n\nDepois do Login o `token` fica guardado automaticamente.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3001" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "2" },
    { "key": "username", "value": "sky" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "sky@example.com" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "password123" },
    { "key": "tweetId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "commentId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "targetUserId", "value": "3" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Geral",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Raiz API",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Para criar conta e fazer login usa sempre esta pasta.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup (criar conta)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (json.user?.username) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('username', json.user.username);",
                  "}",
                  "if (json.user?.email) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('email', json.user.email);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"A minha conta\",\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup",
            "description": "Altera as variáveis da collection: username, email, password. Depois podes fazer Login com os mesmos dados."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (username)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado. Podes usar os outros pedidos.');",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.log('Sem token. Verifica username/password ou cria conta com Signup.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "description": "Login com nome de utilizador. Usa o mesmo username e password do Signup ou do site."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (email)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar utilizadores",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Feed A seguir",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/feed/following"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Por username",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/username/{{username}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Timeline perfil",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/username/{{username}}/timeline"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Por ID",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar utilizador (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"User Admin\",\n  \"username\": \"user_admin\",\n  \"email\": \"admin_criado@vg.local\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"user\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users",
            "description": "Requer token de admin. Password min. 6 caracteres (agora com hash)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar utilizador",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nome atualizado\",\n  \"bio\": \"Bio VG\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Apagar utilizador",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Follow toggle",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/follow"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Following de um user",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/following"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tweets",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar tweets",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tweets"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{username}}", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "userId", "value": "{{userId}}", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Tweet por ID",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets/{{tweetId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar tweet",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Tweet de teste Postman\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar tweet com imagem",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "content", "value": "Tweet com imagem", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "image", "type": "file", "src": [] }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar tweet",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Tweet editado\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets/{{tweetId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Apagar tweet",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets/{{tweetId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Like toggle",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets/{{tweetId}}/like"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Retweet toggle",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tweets/{{tweetId}}/retweet"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Comments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar comentarios",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Por tweet",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments/tweet/{{tweetId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Por ID",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments/{{commentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar comentario",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Comentario teste\",\n  \"tweetId\": {{tweetId}}\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar comentario",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Comentario editado\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments/{{commentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Apagar comentario",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments/{{commentId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Chat",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Conversas",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mensagens",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/chat/with/{{targetUserId}}/messages"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Enviar mensagem",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"content\": \"Ola!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/chat/with/{{targetUserId}}/messages"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Upload",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload imagem",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [{ "key": "image", "type": "file", "src": [] }]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/upload"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  }
}
